    "The anchor frame and anchor point are removed based on fixed spatial position and the method relies on a learnable vector for prediction instead.",
    "Because of their simplicity and flexibility, query-based methods have become a new solution for TAD.",
    "Tan et al. (2021) argue that long-term time-context modeling is critical for proposal generation.",
    "Viewing the video as a time series and using the transformer architecture to model global one-dimensional dependencies can improve location performance.",
    "In their paper, Tan et al. propose two key problems, namely the feature full degree (Zhang and Tao 2012) and time boundary ambiguity (Satkin and Hebert 2010)."
